                    "description": "* Geospatial database design, mapping, standardization and consulting for mobile GIS (field mapping) projects aiming at the collection and analysis of Process Safety, HSSE, and Proactive Maintenance related data. User documentation, support and overall training.\n\n*Supervise and perform application and workflow testing, delivering user work instructions and tailored training for the global O&G Exploration and GIS community. \n\n* Delivering cross platform collaboration and data interoperability solutions. \n\n* Change Management and Communications\n\n* Knowledge Management Services and content creation\n\n* Organizing and hosting the global Mobile GIS webcasts, sharing expertise and progress with >150 global GIS users and management staff while promoting the use of mobile GIS presenting and reporting on new workflows and successful use cases.\n\n* Leading the global TDM&WF  Process Safety Network promoting best practice replication and coordinating the HSSE culture and checks in her directorate. Continuous Improvement Focal Point",
                    "title": "Geomatics Workflow Consultant",
                    "employment_type": "Full-time"
