                    "company": "Shell",
                    "description": "* Managed effectively and with agility all PM activities, stakeholders, communications, timelines, risks and budget in a complex yet very critical project for Shell, acquainted with measurements of data quality at operational asset locations. The expected turnover applying the suggested strategy is in the range of 20mln per year.\n\n* Led the initiative of business analytics and business metrics for all the technical data-related activities in the IT innovation portfolio. The initiative resulted in a leaner work process and a 20% reduction of man hours spent in manual analysis. The metrics have been used as project KPIs and for analytics purposes.\n\n*Set up and maintained the team VSTS dashboard for project and task planning.",
                    "title": "Data Maturation and Integration Lead",
                    "employment_type": "Full-time"
                },
                {
                    "location": "The Hague Area, Netherlands",
                    "date": {
